@startuml ContextOS_Vector_Search_Flow
skinparam backgroundColor #f8f9fa

title Vector Search Flow

participant "Client" as CLIENT
participant "SearchController" as CTRL
participant "VectorSearchService" as VSVC
participant "EmbeddingService" as EMB
participant "OllamaClient" as OLL
database "pgvector\n(PostgreSQL)" as PG

== Query Processing ==
CLIENT -> CTRL : POST /api/v1/search\n{ query: "machine learning\nbooks", type: "SEMANTIC" }

CTRL -> VSVC : search(embedding, filters, limit)

CTRL -> EMB : generateEmbedding("machine learning books")
EMB -> OLL : POST /api/embed
note right: Model: nomic-embed-text\nInput: "machine learning books"

OLL --> EMB : [0.023, -0.145, 0.567, ...]
note right: 768-dimensional float vector

EMB --> CTRL : float[768] queryVector

== Vector Search ==
CTRL -> VSVC : similaritySearch(queryVector, userId, limit=20)
VSVC -> PG : SELECT id, title, type,\n       1 - (embedding <=> ?) AS similarity\nFROM containers\nWHERE owner_id = ?\n  AND embedding IS NOT NULL\nORDER BY embedding <=> ?\nLIMIT 20

note right of PG : IVFFlat index with\nlists=100, probes=10

PG --> VSVC : 20 results with scores

== Post-Processing ==
VSVC -> VSVC : Filter by status != DELETED
VSVC -> VSVC : Apply additional filters
VSVC -> VSVC : Load highlights from content
VSVC --> CTRL : List<SearchResult>

CTRL -> CTRL : Build SearchResponse
CTRL --> CLIENT : 200 OK
note right: Response time: ~150ms

== Index Configuration ==
note over PG : IVFFlat Index\nlists: 100 (sqrt(n) for 10k vectors)\nprobes: 10 (for 90% recall)\nDistance: cosine

@enduml
